          <attvalue for="4" value="1.0" />
          <attvalue for="5" value="Due to his repeated attempts to bring attention to the issue, Leech is now regularly described as the &quot;architect&quot; of Turing's pardon and subsequently the Alan Turing Law, which went on to secure pardons for 75,000 other men and women." />
